Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases where the declaration is resubmitted
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases where declarations are eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Payment Handled' in cases that reach completion
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' after 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases that are corrected and approved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Total time it takes for cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to be finalized either through approval or final rejection
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases where the employee resubmits
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time for a case to be closed after 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' considering both approvals and final rejections
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case
